</span></p><p class="sc-hGMjVM kxdODp pf-200_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-9a1ed3b1-2473-4dd3-9ad0-52b4a022d115"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/online-statutory-mandatory-training-courses" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">Click here</span></span></em></a></span></span></span> to see online courses and resources to help comply with statutory and mandatory training requirements for health and social care professionals.
